data.title: YouTube App - App Store YouTube TV - Watch & DVR Live Sports, Shows & News YouTube Help - Google Help
data.description: Get the official YouTube app on iPhones and iPads. See what the world is watching -- from the hottest music videos to what’s popular in gaming, fashion, beauty, news, learning and more. YouTube TV lets you stream live and local sports, news, shows from 100+ channels including CBS, FOX, NBC, HGTV, TNT, and more. We’ve got complete local network coverage in over 98% of US TV... Find answers to common questions and issues about YouTube, such as how to watch, upload, edit, monetize, and manage your account and channel. Learn from YouTube experts, creators, and community members in the help forum and videos.
